      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示FinTech_TransactionQueue项目里从main分支合并到未开发分支的过程。标题就定为\"Merge from main onto undeveloped branch\"，整体用从左到右的布局。",
