    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，develop分支更准确。流程应该是：先有初始commit，然后从main切出develop分支，develop上做一个commit，同时main也继续往前走一个commit，最后把main合并回develop。这样比较符合实际工作流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout main",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
