      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来构建这个结构。先设置标题和LR布局，然后画出main上的初始commit，接着切出develop分支并提交，再切回main做第二个commit，最后回到develop执行merge main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph LR",
